  "texts": [
    "Silver nitrate (ACS reagent, ≥99.0%), 4-decylaniline (97%), p-toluenesulfonic acid monohydrate, bovine serum albumin (≥98%), ethanol, wastewater (ERM-CA616), soil (Chromium VI -Soil, RTC CRM041-030), synthetic seawater (SSWS30) and tetrahydrofuran (≥ 99.9%) were purchased from Sigma Aldrich and used without additional purification.",
    "Tert-butyl nitrite (>90.0%) was purchased from TCI Chemicals.",
    "Humic acid (practical grade) was purchased from Fujifilm Wako.",
    "Marine sediments with polychlorinated biphenyls and organochlorine pesticides (NMIJ CRM-7304-a) was purchased from the National Metrology Institute of Japan.",
    "Polystyrene-b-poly(ethylene oxide) diblock copolymers with M w 18,000 g mol -1 (PS) and M w 7500 g mol -1 (PEO) molecular weight subunits were acquired from Polymer Source (PS 18000 -b-PEO 7500)."
